{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "eng-quality-engineer-technical-emergency-9mo1",
    "category": "pro/engineering/quality_engineer",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9MO1aY1xC80",
    "mode": "srt"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't think we can do that.",
      "zh": "我覺得我們做不到。",
      "ja": "それはできないと思います。",
      "time": "00:00:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, no, no, no.",
      "zh": "喔，不，不，不。",
      "ja": "ああ、いや、いや、いや。",
      "time": "00:00:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm lost!",
      "zh": "我迷路了！",
      "ja": "迷子になった！",
      "time": "00:00:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Where's the Lord?",
      "zh": "領主在哪裡？",
      "ja": "領主はどこ？",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's just really...",
      "zh": "真的就是...",
      "ja": "本当に...",
      "time": "00:00:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Dude, what do I do?",
      "zh": "老兄，我該怎麼辦？",
      "ja": "おい、どうすればいい？",
      "time": "00:00:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hell!",
      "zh": "糟糕！",
      "ja": "最悪！",
      "time": "00:00:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Will we stuck here forever?",
      "zh": "我們會永遠被困在這裡嗎？",
      "ja": "ここにずっと閉じ込められるの？",
      "time": "00:00:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do not panic.",
      "zh": "不要慌張。",
      "ja": "慌てるな。",
      "time": "00:00:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do not panic.",
      "zh": "不要慌張。",
      "ja": "慌てるな。",
      "time": "00:00:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We are trained for professionals.",
      "zh": "我們是受過專業訓練的。",
      "ja": "私たちはプロの訓練を受けている。",
      "time": "00:00:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now stay calm.",
      "zh": "現在保持冷靜。",
      "ja": "今は落ち着け。",
      "time": "00:00:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We are going around the leaf.",
      "zh": "我們要繞過這片葉子。",
      "ja": "葉っぱの周りを回る。",
      "time": "00:00:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Around the leaf?",
      "zh": "繞過葉子？",
      "ja": "葉っぱの周り？",
      "time": "00:00:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't think we can do that.",
      "zh": "我覺得我們做不到。",
      "ja": "それはできないと思います。",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, nonsense.",
      "zh": "喔，胡說。",
      "ja": "そんな馬鹿な。",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is nothing compared to the twig of 93.",
      "zh": "這跟93年的小枝比起來算不了什麼。",
      "ja": "これは93年の小枝に比べたら何でもない。",
      "time": "00:00:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's it.",
      "zh": "就是這樣。",
      "ja": "それだ。",
      "time": "00:00:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's it.",
      "zh": "就是這樣。",
      "ja": "それだ。",
      "time": "00:00:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good.",
      "zh": "很好。",
      "ja": "いいぞ。",
      "time": "00:00:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're doing great.",
      "zh": "你做得很好。",
      "ja": "よくやっている。",
      "time": "00:00:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There you go.",
      "zh": "就這樣。",
      "ja": "そうだ。",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Here you go.",
      "zh": "給你。",
      "ja": "はい、どうぞ。",
      "time": "00:00:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Watch my eyes.",
      "zh": "看著我的眼睛。",
      "ja": "私の目を見て。",
      "time": "00:00:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't look away.",
      "zh": "不要移開視線。",
      "ja": "目をそらすな。",
      "time": "00:00:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And here's the line again.",
      "zh": "線又來了。",
      "ja": "そしてまたラインだ。",
      "time": "00:01:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝你。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:01:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you, Mr. Sorrell.",
      "zh": "謝謝你，索雷爾先生。",
      "ja": "ありがとう、ソレルさん。",
      "time": "00:01:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good job, everybody.",
      "zh": "大家做得好。",
      "ja": "みんな、よくやった。",
      "time": "00:01:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, my.",
      "zh": "喔，我的天。",
      "ja": "ああ、まあ。",
      "time": "00:01:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "There's quite a gap, Mr. Sorrell.",
      "zh": "索雷爾先生，這裡有很大的縫隙。",
      "ja": "ソレルさん、かなり隙間があります。",
      "time": "00:01:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Shouldn't we tell the queen?",
      "zh": "我們不應該告訴女王嗎？",
      "ja": "女王に知らせるべきでは？",
      "time": "00:01:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I don't think we need to involve the queen in this.",
      "zh": "我覺得不需要讓女王參與這件事。",
      "ja": "これに女王を巻き込む必要はないと思う。",
      "time": "00:01:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "She's got enough on her plate already.",
      "zh": "她已經有很多事情要處理了。",
      "ja": "彼女はすでに多くのことで手一杯だ。",
      "time": "00:01:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Treating her daughter.",
      "zh": "還要照顧她的女兒。",
      "ja": "娘の治療もしている。",
      "time": "00:01:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, yes, Princess Adam.",
      "zh": "喔，是的，亞當公主。",
      "ja": "ああ、そうだ、アダム姫。",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The poor dear.",
      "zh": "可憐的孩子。",
      "ja": "かわいそうな子だ。",
      "time": "00:01:19"
    }
  ]
}